BUT NOW THERE ARE WARNING SIGNS
THAT IT IS ALL ABOUT TO CHANGE.

00:00:24.130 --> 00:00:27.070
I VIEW THE CHALLENGE ON
THE FOOD FRONT AS PERHAPS

00:00:27.070 --> 00:00:30.930
THE LEADING CHALLENGE
FACING HUMANITY TODAY.

