00:11:32.630 --> 00:11:35.100
>>THE REMAINS OF THE
HUNDREDS OF ANIMALS

00:11:35.100 --> 00:11:37.570
CHIEF SAMMY HAS
LOST TO DROUGHT

00:11:37.570 --> 00:11:40.470
OVER THE LAST FEW
YEARS ARE NEARBY.

00:11:40.470 --> 00:11:44.500
A CONSTANT REMINDER
OF WHAT HE HAS LOST.

00:11:44.500 --> 00:11:47.230
THIS CALF DIED IN APRIL.

