AND WHAT IT DOES TO ME
IS MAKE IT VERY DIFFICULT

00:14:36.830 --> 00:14:39.000
TO DECIDE WHAT
TO GROW NEXT YEAR.

00:14:39.000 --> 00:14:42.070
AND THAT WILL
AFFECT THE YIELD.

00:14:42.070 --> 00:14:45.330
>>MANY BELIEVE THAT THE
VOLATILITY IN THE GRAIN MARKETS

00:14:45.330 --> 00:14:50.530
IS THE RESULT, AT LEAST IN
PART, OF CLIMATE CHANGE.

00:14:50.530 --> 00:14:53.530
WHETHER YOU CALL IT GLOBAL
WARMING OR GLOBAL CHANGE,

00:14:53.530 --> 00:14:56.000
IT'S CERTAINLY HAVING
WHAT I THINK IS HAVING

00:14:56.000 --> 00:14:59.600
A SIGNIFICANT EFFECT IN
TERMS OF THIS VOLATILITY.

00:14:59.600 --> 00:15:02.370


