WHAT WE'VE HAD IS A VERY WET
AND COLD WINTER AFTER A RUN OF

00:15:13.070 --> 00:15:17.070
VERY MILD WINTERS, AND IT'S THIS
CHANGEABILITY, THIS VOLATILITY.

00:15:17.070 --> 00:15:19.900
YOU KNOW, WE SEEM TO SET
ANOTHER METEOROLOGICAL

00:15:19.900 --> 00:15:22.270
RECORD EVERY OTHER
MONTH THESE DAYS

