IF WE KEEP GROWING AS WE ARE,
WE'LL NEED TWO OR THREE PLANETS

00:15:41.230 --> 00:15:45.070
NEVER MIND ONE.

00:15:45.070 --> 00:15:48.500
>>SO EVEN IN MORE TEMPERATE
PARTS OF THE WORLD,

